header.title: IT Professional with experience in software development, data analytics and working agile
intro_1: I am an IT Professional with experience in Agile software development and engineering, data science, AI, robotics, and cloud computing. I have been involved in designing and developing IT systems both backend and frontend. I am passionate about Agile thinking and way of working, which is the reason why I got certified as a Scrum Master and assisted application of Agile principles in Siemens.
intro_2: Besides my technical passion, I take all opportunities to develop a business understanding in IT. I am interested in developing a technology-business mind to be able both to understand and develop IT systems but also to collaborate with non-technical people and understand business applications. I am all about automation, digitalization and business optimization.
intro_3: Education-wise, I am an IT engineer and have a Master's in IT Business with focus on data science. Job-wise, I am interested in working with ambitious, talented & collaborative people in companies which value employees and create a difference.
